the production, followed by the movie itself at 6. The amazing cast
of this 1962 D-Day epic includes John Wayne, Robert Mitchum, Henry
Fonda, Rod Steiger, Robert Ryan, Peter Lawford, Richard Burton,
Richard Beymer, Jeffrey Hunter and Sal Mineo.
</P>
