   ``The Thomas Crown Affair,'' Showtime Saturday at 9: Cable
premiere of the surprisingly well-liked 1999 remake starring Pierce
Brosnan and Rene Russo in the roles originated by Steve McQueen and
Faye Dunaway. Brosnan is the rich, thrill-seeking thief, and Russo
is the woman who may or may not catch him. Dunaway has a cameo as a
shrink.
</P>
<P>
   NFL Football, ESPN Sunday at 8:30: Tennessee at Buffalo kicks
