   LIFESTYLE
</P>
<P>
   COXNET LIFESTYLES PAGE
</P>
<P>
   COXNET LIFESTYLES 0902: DIAPER BAGS TO DROOL FOR _ A roomy,
well-designed diaper bag can make your life a lot easier and keep
that tot well-stocked with baby must-haves when you're both on the
run. That old-fashioned frilly, pink-and-blue quilted diaper bag
your mother dragged around is pretty much a relic of the past.
Today's versions run the gamut from rough and tumble nylon backpack
to sleek and sexy satin looks brandishing tony designer monikers
and matching price tags (Morrow, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art
includes eight 18-pica color photographs of diaper bags.
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   BUYING HEALTH INSURANCE _ Call it a ``rite of passage'' _ one of
those things nearly everyone must do after they retire or turn 65 _
but choosing health insurance can be complicated and confusing for
seniors. (Allmon, Waco Herald-Tribune) Art includes a 1-column
color photo illustration of a woman looking over policies.
</P>
<P>
   YARD SALES _ Let's talk about yard sales, because there's a lot
to say. Well, actually, all that really needs to be said is that
people have yard sales and people buy things at yard sales. That's
it. (Sauer, Grand Junction Daily Sentinel)
</P>
