documentary tribute to the first Jewish baseball star,
writer-director Aviva Kempner could not have intended it as a
metaphor for the current barrier-shattering campaign bid of
Orthodox Jewish Sen. Joseph Lieberman. (Erstein, Plam Beach Post).
35.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-HANK _ ``The Life and Times of Hank Greenberg.'' Review of
the documentary about Jewish baseball great. (Ringel, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   KEMPNER-INTERVIEW _ Interview with documentary filmmaker Aviva
Kempner, director of ``The Life and Times of Hank Greenberg.''
(Murray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-WONDERLAND _ ``Wonderland.'' The drabs of London. Grade:
B. (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-AFFAIR _ Movie review: ``An Affair of Love.'' (Ringel,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-STEVE _ Movie review: ``The Tao of Steve.'' Ineffectual
guy movie. Grade: C-.(Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
