attratctive show in betwen major exhibits to deep the visitors
coming. how does it work? (Fox, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 26.
</P>
<P>
   SOUL-POSSESSED _ ATLANTA _ Mini-review of ``Soul Possessed'',
which opened Wednesday in Atlanta. The Debbie Allen-directed dance
drama about mysticism and a woman torn between two men, is a
