<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ In his speech accepting the Democratic
vice-presidential nomination, Joseph Lieberman made one of his
customary swipes at the gratuitous sex and violence coming out of
Hollywood. ``In many Americans,'' he told delegates at the party
convention in Los Angeles earlier this month, ``there is a swelling
sense that our standards of decency and civility have eroded.''
Well, Senator Lieberman's worst nightmre has just come to
life....By Andrew Gumbel, The Independent &QL;
