<P>
   FILM-AFFAIR &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ ``An Affair of Love's'' original title was ``Une
Liaison Pornographique,'' and you don't have to be fluent in French
to know the literal translation of that. It's a good thing the
title was changed, because _ despite some tastefully filmed sex
scenes that wouldn't raise an eyebrow from anyone who's ever seen
``Sex and the City'' _ the movie is nowhere as salacious as ``A
Pornographic Affair'' would indicate. The bad news is that it is as
generic as the new English-language title would indicate. By ROBERT
PHILPOT. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   F I N A N C I A L &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
