   BIZBOOKS-REVIEWS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ The goal of Mark Van Osnabrugge and Robert J.
Robinson's ``Angel Investing'' is to establish a sort of mutual
admiration society between entrepreneurs and investors. It educates
readers in each category to the opportunities the other category
offers and guides them through the process of joining forces for
mutual benefit. By CLAUDE CROWLEY. Story has moved in ``f''
financial category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
