<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-ALBUM-OF-THE-WEEK-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   ALBUM-OF-THE-WEEK (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Aug. 31.
</P>
