<P>
   (NYT25) UNDATED -- Aug. 31, 2000 -- BUYER'S-EDGE-COX-2 -- With
many of us lugging briefcases, cellphones, Palm Pilots, laptops,
lunch boxes and handbags, leaving the house is no lightweight task
these days. Add a baby and you've got your hands, and arms, full. A
roomy, well-designed diaper bag could make your life a lot easier
and keep that tot well-stocked with baby must-haves when you're
both on the run. The Eddie Bauer diaber bag, left, and the Kate
Spade diaper bag. (Parker C. Smith/Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT24) UNDATED -- Aug. 31, 2000 -- BUYER'S-EDGE-COX-1 -- With
