rubble of a fast-moving, spectacular fire that engulfed the
construction site of a waterfront condominium complex and destroyed
nine homes and an apartment building late Wednesday. An aerial view
of the devastation Thursday as firefighters continued to spray
water on hot spots. (Keith Meyers/The New York Times)
